# Loan and Savings Interest Calculator

Welcome to the **Loan and Savings Interest Calculator** project! This Python program is designed to help you calculate loan payments (non-deposit) and savings interest (deposit) using simple and compound interest formulas. Whether you are managing personal finances or working on a financial project, this tool will provide accurate and flexible calculations.

